title: Friday Morning Conversation With Brothers Osborne + Bobby Is Taking Morgan #2 To Dinner + Show Member Got Into Car Accident
itunes:title: Friday Morning Conversation With Brothers Osborne + Bobby Is Taking Morgan #2 To Dinner + Show Member Got Into Car Accident
description:
Brothers Osborne stop by the show to celebrate the release of their latest album "Port Saint Joe" which is out today! Bobby tells us about his plans to take Morgan #2 out to dinner. A member of the show recaps their recent car accident.
